        <div class="text-blg tracking-wide text-black dark:text-white text-opacity-85 dark:text-opacity-85 font-mono font-light"><b>Role:</b><br>Designer</div>
        <div class="text-blg tracking-wide text-black dark:text-white text-opacity-85 dark:text-opacity-85 font-mono font-light"><b>Timeline:</b><br>5 Weeks</div>
