                  <div class="text-white dark:text-black text-opacity-75 dark:text-opacity-75 font-mono text-bsm md:text-blg"><a href="https://www.are.na/ethan-wright" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Are.na</a></div>
                  <div class="text-white dark:text-black text-opacity-75 dark:text-opacity-75 font-mono text-bsm md:text-blg"><a href="https://www.behance.net/theethanwright" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Behance</a></div>
